          <h3>General Rules :-</h3>
          <p>
            <b>1. Eligibility:</b><br>
             Participants must be registered for the competition by the designated deadline.<br>
             No age limit.<br>
             Participants can of any college.<br>
            <b>2. Time Limit:</b><br>
