             Costumes must be appropriate and not oensive or indecent.<br>
             Participants are responsible for their own props and costumes.<br>
            <b>3. Music:</b><br>
             Music must be submitted in advance in the specified format (e.g., MP3).<br>
             Songs with explicit or inappropriate lyrics are prohibited.<br>
          </p>
          
